                            <p class="text-break white-space-pre-line">Reference: CAW004768-TT-1Branch Manager (Plant Hire) - Northern Cape - Kathu A new Plant Hire Branch is opening up in Kathu (Northern Cape) and our client has an opening for a Branch Manager.This is a high pressure position and requires an individual who has at least 3 years Branch Manager experience in the Plant Hire or alternatively Civils, Construction or Mining Industries.Requirements: Diploma / Degree in Business Management or similar will be an added benefit Strong sales and customer service skills Must have a valid drivers license and be will to travel to other branches Good understanding and working experience of MS Excel Strong communication skills and the ability to inspire and lead a team Generate above-average sales for the business (target driven) Self assured and motivated with a relentless drive to succeed Possess a good level of technical knowledge and proficiency in order to evaluate the workshop output Salary:Negotiable Basic Salary  Company Benefits Company Vehicle and Fuel Allowance  Branch profit share.Please note only candidates with the required experience will be contacted and considered. If you are not contacted within 14 days, kindly consider your application unsuccessful.Visit our website for more opportunities: www.sydsenrecruit.com (Follow us on LinkedIn, Instagram or Facebook)SYDSEN RECRUIT - THE NEXT LEVEL OF RECRUITMENT Negotiable - Monthly</p>
