                            <p class="text-break white-space-pre-line">I am looking for an Entrepreneurial minded individual to join Liberty as a Professional Financial Advisor. Financial advisors are sales driven professionals with a passion for prospecting, advising and servicing medium to high net wealth clients with a specific focus on their Risk, Retirement Annuities, Investments and Estates planning needs. This long term career is ideal for a sales driven individual to establish and grow a client book as well as build a franchise under the Liberty banner. Requirements: - Grade 12 - Valid drivers licence and own reliable transport Further to meeting all the requirements, the following criteria would be essential: - Entrepreneurial mind-set - An established network of clients and ability to prospect for new business Even if you do not have industry experience, our comprehensive training programme and on-going mentoring, will provide you with the knowledge and skills to be successful. For more information on this exciting profession or to set up an appointment to hear about our value proposition, which is undoubtedly the best in the market, please feel free to contact me on Janeen.Jordaanliberty.co.za</p>
